{"tid":2152695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度擬強制分享非個人數據法例 要求 FB、Google、Amazon 提供資料","createTime":"2020-08-12T06:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T17:58:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd378a3332847d536bae89c48568932b51f6fade","tid":2152695,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"根據路透社報道，印度非個人數據治理框架專家委員會在 7 月提議立法，政府、初創企業和其他實體可以出於國家安全、經濟和公共利益目的，要求印度任何公司公開非個人數據。為此，印度有意設立非個人數據管理局（NPDA）作為監管機構，NPDA 有權決定公民或組織是否可以從印度任何公司獲取專有的非個人數據。<br />\n<br />\n根據消息人士提供的信件内容顯示，印度要求 Amazon、Facebook、Google 提供匿名及非個人用戶數據，以協助科技生態圈業務發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/12/india-nonperson/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F12%2Findia-nonperson%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf%2Fuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=f6268a89\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/12/india-nonperson/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"f4a3e5750215a2780374b22fe1ca84f2fe18df21","tid":2152695,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T00:03:54.000Z","msg":"印仔開始學某國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffd25235f9c171972c565e9fe016d53176d1f90","tid":2152695,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"無計唔咁做咪慢慢比人食埋個國家<br />\n千年難得一次叫價機會"}]}